                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On July 25 at 3 p.m., the United Nations Security Council met for the first time
                    since July 7; for the record of the July 25th session, see U.N. document
                    S/PV.477. During this meeting, Ambassador Austin read the text (U.N. document
                    S/1626) of the first report submitted to the Security Council by the United
                    States Government, under date of July 24, 1950, in accordance with the Security
                    Council resolution of July 7.</p>
            </div>
